law.text:
A public health and clinical laboratory shall provide services in connection with:
Any inquiry that the Department or any health officer or physician makes about a communicable disease;
Any inquiry that the Department makes about sewage;
Any inquiry that the Department makes about a trade waste;
Any inquiry the Department makes about a nuisance;
Any examination or analysis of a water supply;
Any examination or analysis of milk; and
Any inquiry about any other matter that the Secretary requires.
